{"GYL55zQzQkF":{"id":"GYL55zQzQkF","type":"work","title":"北墅抱甕錄","authors":[{"name":"高士奇","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《北墅抱甕錄》•一卷","author_info":"國朝高士奇撰","summary":"國朝高士奇撰。士奇有《春秋地名考略》，已著錄。此書前有康熙庚午自序，乃其告歸後所作，北墅者，所居別業之名也。墅中蒔植花木頗多，士奇因取果樹卉竹蔬茹藥蔓之類，各疏其形色品狀，以為此編，凡二百二十二種，其敘錄頗為詳備。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=645290","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095478","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙刻本","version":"v1","total_page":109,"paragraph_count":983,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zzJSjZ":{"id":"GYL55zzJSjZ","type":"work","title":"鬻子","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《鬻子》•一卷","author_info":"舊本題周鬻熊撰","summary":"舊本題周鬻熊撰。《崇文總目》作十四篇，高似孫《子略》作十二篇，陳振孫《書錄解題》稱陸佃所校十五篇。此本題唐逢行珪注，凡十四篇，蓋即《崇文總目》所著錄也。考《漢書•藝文志》道家《鬻子說》二十二篇，又小說家《鬻子說》十九篇，是當時本有二書。《列子》引《鬻子》凡三條，皆黃、老清靜之說，與今本不類。疑即道家二十二篇之文。今本所載與賈誼《新書》所引六條文格略同，疑即小說家之《鬻子》說也。杜預《左傳注》，稱鬻熊為祝融十二世孫。孔穎達疏謂不知出何書。《史記》載鬻熊子事文王，早卒其子曰熊麗，熊麗生熊狂，熊狂生熊繹。成王時舉文、武勤勞之後嗣，受封於楚。《漢書》載魏相奏記霍光，稱文王見鬻子，年九十餘。雖所說小異，然大約文、武時人。今其書乃有昔者魯周公語，又有昔者魯周公使康叔往守於殷語，而賈誼《新書》亦引其成王問答凡五條，時代殊不相及。劉勰《文心雕龍》雲，鬻熊知道，文王諮詢。遺文餘事，錄為《鬻子》。則裒輯成編，不出熊手。流傳附益，或構虛詞，故《漢志》別入小說家歟？獨是偽《四八目》一書見北齊陽休之序錄，凡古來帝王輔佐有數可紀者，靡不具載。而此書所列禹七大夫皋陶、杜子業、既子、施子黯、季子甯、然子堪、輕子玉，湯七大夫慶誧、伊尹、湟裏且、東門虛、南門蝡、西門疵、北門側，皆具有姓名，獨不見收。似乎六朝之末尚無此本。或唐以來好事之流依仿賈誼所引，撰為贗本，亦未可知。觀其標題甲乙，故為佚脫錯亂之狀，而誼書所引則無一條之偶合，豈非有心相避，而巧匿其文，使讀者互相檢驗，生其信心歟？且其篇名冗贅，古無此體，又每篇寥寥數言，詞旨膚淺，決非三代舊文。姑以流傳既久，存備一家耳。卷首有逢行珪序及永徽四年進書表，自署華州鄭縣尉。裏居未詳。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"},{"source":"漢書藝文志","source_bid":"GY2rqZp8Hvw","title_info":"鬻子二十二篇","summary":""}],"books":["CXVzwdUt8XH"],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/鬻子","type":"text"},{"id":"wikisource-siku","name":"维基文库（四庫全書本）","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/鬻子_(四庫全書本)","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText（原典）","url":"https://ctext.org/yuzi/zh","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=187118","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=386399","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-shanghaihanfenlouyin","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/DZ1171","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"上海涵芬樓影印明《正統道藏》本","version":"v3","total_page":58,"paragraph_count":288,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-sikuquanshuben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/SK1757","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"四庫全書本","version":"v2","total_page":68,"paragraph_count":295,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-mingkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ8921298205899","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明刻本","version":"v1","total_page":38,"paragraph_count":222,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zZcDKd":{"id":"GYL55zZcDKd","type":"work","title":"虎薈","authors":[{"name":"陳繼儒","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《虎薈》•六卷","author_info":"明陳繼儒撰","summary":"明陳繼儒撰。繼儒有《邵康節外紀》，已著錄。是編末有黃庭鳳跋，謂繼儒病瘧，王穉登貽以虎苑一帙佩之，而瘧愈，遂為是書。凡所引用，多拉雜無倫。若《周禮》司尊彝，裸用虎彝、蜼彝，《漢書》履虎尾絇履之類，與談虎無涉，亦皆漫為牽綴，真所謂無關體要者也。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":6},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/虎薈","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=671082","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6279","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v7","total_page":312,"paragraph_count":281,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055974","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v2","total_page":306,"paragraph_count":2429,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zC4htB":{"id":"GYL55zC4htB","type":"work","title":"花史左編","authors":[{"name":"王路","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《花史左編》•二十七卷","author_info":"明王路撰","summary":"明王路撰。路字仲遵，嘉興人。此書皆載花之品目故實，分類編輯。屬辭隸事，多涉佻纖，不出明季小品之習。《浙江通志》載王路《花史》二十四卷，有天啟元年李日華序。今此本二十七卷，無日華序，而前有陳繼儒序，與路所作小引，皆稱二十四卷。又此本二十五卷花之友，二十七卷花之器，皆題潭雲宣猷馭雲子補，二十二卷花麈，題百花主人輯。則路書本二十四卷，此三卷乃後人所補入，而刊書者並為一目耳。又路小序稱此書為左編，別有右編為花之辭翰，約一十二卷，蓋有其名而未成書者也。","edition":"江蘇巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":27},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=881713","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5485077","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY1354","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v22","total_page":938,"paragraph_count":2842,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA06513","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本","version":"v1","total_page":4,"paragraph_count":28,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055961","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v5","total_page":948,"paragraph_count":2487,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zFdcXh":{"id":"GYL55zFdcXh","type":"work","title":"花史","authors":[{"name":"吳彥匡","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《花史》•十卷","author_info":"明吳彥匡撰","summary":"明吳彥匡撰。彥匡爵裏未詳。是書蓋本常熟蔣養菴《花編》，松江曹介人《花品》二書推而廣之，得百有餘種，每一花為一類，各加神品、妙品、佳品、能品、具品、逸品標目，附以前人遺事及詠花詩歌。大都以意為之，所品第不必皆確也。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=908050","type":"text","details":"不著撰者"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095416","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v2","total_page":194,"paragraph_count":182,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zN7otT":{"id":"GYL55zN7otT","type":"work","title":"倦圃蒔植記","authors":[{"name":"曹溶","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《倦圃蒔植記》•三卷","author_info":"國朝曹溶撰","summary":"國朝曹溶撰。溶有《崇禎五十宰相傳》，已著錄。茲編乃溶自山西陽和道歸裏，築室范蠡湖上，名曰倦圃，多植花木其間，因記其圃中所有。分花卉二卷，竹樹一卷，各疏其名品故實，及種植之法。溶學本贍博，故引據多有可觀，惟下語頗涉纖仄，尚未脫明季小品積習。前有自序，題康熙甲子。案溶卒於康熙二十四年乙丑，年八十三，則此書乃其晚年遊戲之筆也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/倦圃蒔植記","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=557730","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=566439","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055969","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":188,"paragraph_count":164,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095479","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"抄本","version":"v4","total_page":187,"paragraph_count":1066,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zTpKkb":{"id":"GYL55zTpKkb","type":"work","title":"名花譜","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《名花譜》•一卷","author_info":"舊本題西湖居易主人撰","summary":"舊本題西湖居易主人撰，不著名氏，亦無序跋。其書雜抄《群芳譜》之類而成，蓋近人作。所列凡九十二種，而附以瓶花訣、盆種訣、十二月花木訣。所言種植之法，掛漏不詳，間附故實，尤冗雜無緒。觀其開卷敘梅一段，字句凡鄙，引用謬誤，不過粗識文義之人，偶然抄錄成冊耳。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3089316","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055972","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v2","total_page":131,"paragraph_count":89,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55z99RAw":{"id":"GYL55z99RAw","type":"work","title":"汝南圃史","authors":[{"name":"周文華","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《汝南圃史》•十二卷","author_info":"明周文華撰","summary":"明周文華撰。文華字含章，蘇州人。前有萬曆庚申陳元素序，稱之曰光祿君。不知為光祿何官也。文華自序，稱因見允齋《花史》，嫌其未備，補葺是書。凡分月令栽種花果、木果、水果、木本花、條刺花、草木花、竹木草、蔬菜、瓜豆十二門，皆敍述栽種之法，間以詩詞。大抵就江南所有言之，故河北蘋婆，嶺表荔支之屬，亦不著錄。較他書剽剟陳言，侈陳珍怪者較為切實。惟分部多有未確，如西瓜不入瓜豆而入水果，枸杞不入條刺而入菜蔬，皆非其類。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/汝南圃史","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=7194708","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA09331","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本","version":"v2","total_page":92,"paragraph_count":39,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA06514","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本(序刊)","version":"v6","total_page":752,"paragraph_count":4484,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishudaizhaikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095469","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆書帶齋刻本","version":"v4","total_page":679,"paragraph_count":4594,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55z5dCNs":{"id":"GYL55z5dCNs","type":"work","title":"群芳譜","authors":[{"name":"王象晉","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《群芳譜》•三十卷","author_info":"明王象晉撰","summary":"明王象晉撰。象晉字藎臣，山東新城人。萬曆甲辰進士，官至浙江右布政使。是書凡天譜三卷，歲譜四卷，穀譜一卷，蔬譜二卷，果譜四卷，茶竹譜三卷，桑麻葛苧譜一卷，藥譜三卷，木譜三卷，花譜三卷，卉譜二卷，鶴魚譜一卷。略於種植而詳於療治之法與典故藝文，割裂餖飣，頗無足取。聖祖仁皇帝詔儒臣刪其踳駁，正其舛謬，複為拾遺補闕，成《廣群芳譜》一書，昭示萬世。覆視是編，真已陳之土苴矣。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":30}},"GYL55ziy1YB":{"id":"GYL55ziy1YB","type":"work","title":"蛇譜","authors":[{"name":"陳鼎","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蛇譜》•一卷","author_info":"國朝陳鼎撰","summary":"國朝陳鼎撰。此書記蛇之異者凡六十三則，大抵皆蠻荒異怪之談，不為徵信。其五十三則以後，皆錄《山海經》之文，尤為剿說。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/蛇譜","type":"text"}]},"GYL55zoKbgK":{"id":"GYL55zoKbgK","type":"work","title":"禽蟲述","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《禽蟲述》•一卷","author_info":"舊本題閩中袁達德撰","summary":"舊本題閩中袁達德撰。徐《火勃》《筆精》雲，《山居雜卷》中《禽蟲述》一卷，乃閩中袁達撰。達字德修，程榮署曰袁達德。傳之後世，誰能辨其姓名乎？案《千頃堂書目》載此書，亦雲袁達字德修，閩縣人，正德癸酉舉人，官貴溪縣知縣，降補湖廣都司經歷，與《火勃》語相合。然則此書實出袁達，刊本誤衍德字也。其書述禽蟲名義典故，兼仿《禽經》、《埤雅》之體，聯絡成文，亦或間以排偶，但有章段，不分門目，亦無注釋，不免為餖飣之學。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=600073","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-xieben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA09346","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"写本","version":"v6","total_page":126,"paragraph_count":189,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095493","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"抄本","version":"v2","total_page":138,"paragraph_count":166,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zvYngF":{"id":"GYL55zvYngF","type":"work","title":"烏衣香牒","authors":[{"name":"陳邦彥","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《烏衣香牒》•四卷、《春駒小譜》•二卷","author_info":"國朝陳邦彥撰","summary":"國朝陳邦彥撰。邦彥字世南。此本題匏廬道人，其自號也。海寧人。康熙癸未進士，官至內閣學士兼禮部侍郎。《烏衣香牒》皆采摭燕事。凡分八門，前有乾隆戊午邦彥自序雲，分為三卷。而此多一卷，疑刊刻之時分四卷，以均頁數，而序則未及追改耳。《春駒小譜》皆采摭蝶事，分為五門。蓋欲仿宋人《蟹錄》之例，以為談助。然蒐羅雖廣，而考核多疏。一時寄興之作，固不暇於精審也。","comment":"──右“譜錄類”草木鳥獸蟲魚之屬，三十五部，二百二卷，皆附《存目》。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"related_works":[{"id":"GYLt1FRRkwy","title":"春駒小譜"}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3001530","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055988","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":441,"paragraph_count":980,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zrtWKq":{"id":"GYL55zrtWKq","type":"work","title":"蟲天志","authors":[{"name":"沈宏正","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蟲天志》•十卷","author_info":"明沈宏正撰","summary":"明沈宏正撰。宏正，嘉定人。是書集鳥獸蟲魚異事，分為六部。莊子雲，惟蟲能蟲，惟蟲能天，書之命名蓋取於此。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2358360","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055982","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v6","total_page":573,"paragraph_count":1243,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zfMR3D":{"id":"GYL55zfMR3D","type":"work","title":"晴川蟹錄","authors":[{"name":"孫之騄","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《晴川蟹錄》•四卷、《後錄》•四卷","author_info":"國朝孫之騄撰","summary":"國朝孫之騄撰。之騄所輯《尚書大傳》，已著錄。是編搜采蟹之詩文故實，分譜錄、事錄、文錄、詩錄四門，後錄又分事典、賦詠、食憲、拾遺四門。餖飣掇拾，冗雜無緒，在晴川八識之中，最為下乘。遠不逮傅肱、高似孫二家書也。","edition":"浙江吳玉墀家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"additional_works":[{"book_title":"後錄","n_juan":4}],"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/晴川蟹錄","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=859217","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055977","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v5","total_page":395,"paragraph_count":1811,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keqingchuanbashiben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095505","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻晴川八識本","version":"v3","total_page":136,"paragraph_count":685,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55z2hufd":{"id":"GYL55z2hufd","type":"work","title":"學圃雜疏","authors":[{"name":"王世懋","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《學圃雜疏》•一卷","author_info":"明王世懋撰","summary":"明王世懋撰。世懋有《卻金傳》，已著錄。茲編皆記其圃中所有暨聞見所及者，分花、果、蔬、瓜、豆、竹六類，各疏其品目及栽植之法。大致以花為主，而草木之類則從略。書止一卷，《續說郛》以花疏、果疏各分為卷者非也。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/學圃雜疏","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6326","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v4","total_page":123,"paragraph_count":175,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY5979","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v1","total_page":75,"paragraph_count":611,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zKFD2f":{"id":"GYL55zKFD2f","type":"work","title":"花裏活","authors":[{"name":"陳詩教","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《花裏活》•三卷","author_info":"明陳詩教撰","summary":"明陳詩教撰。詩教字四可，秀水人。是編輯古今花卉故實，按代分編，然皆因襲陳言，別無奇僻，考證尤多疏漏。如雲五代梁有王彥章，吳亦有王彥章，不知楊行密之將乃王茂章，後歸梁改名景仁，並無所謂王彥章者，其舛謬率皆此類。至《花裏活》之名蓋用李賀詩秦宮一生花裏活句，然秦宮何人，而可以援自比乎？失考甚矣。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/花裏活","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=410693","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-xuehaileibian","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CXHLB379","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"學海類編","version":"v4","total_page":115,"paragraph_count":346,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zWjcTq":{"id":"GYL55zWjcTq","type":"work","title":"蠙衣生馬記","authors":[{"name":"郭子章","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蠙衣生馬記》•一卷","author_info":"明郭子章撰","summary":"明郭子章撰。子章有《蠙衣生易解》，已著錄。是編摭載籍中所記馬事，分上、下二篇。援引頗博，皆著所采書名，較明人他說部頗有根據。唯以宛馬為晉泰始時所獻，不知漢時已有之；又以果下馬為出於《魏志》，不知亦載於《漢書》，捃拾未免稍略耳。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4737786","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6328","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v5","total_page":204,"paragraph_count":128,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055973","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v2","total_page":101,"paragraph_count":67,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55zcUpBR":{"id":"GYL55zcUpBR","type":"work","title":"畫眉筆談","authors":[{"name":"陳均","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《畫眉筆談》•一卷","author_info":"國朝陳均撰","summary":"國朝陳均撰。均字康疇，歙縣人。此書皆記豢養畫眉鳥之事，本不足道，然養鷹諸法，古人著錄。姑存其目，以備博物之一端。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/畫眉筆談","type":"text"}]}}